label-studio-ar
Copyright 2026 Khalid Almutairi

This project is an Arabic (RTL) localization overlay for Label Studio.
It does NOT include or modify the Label Studio source code. Instead, it
runs the official Docker image (heartexlabs/label-studio) unchanged and
injects a small client-side script (arabic.js) at runtime via a bind
mount to translate the DOM and apply RTL styling.

